.TH L10N-PREVIEW 1 "2026-02-15" "Daniel Nylander" "L10n Preview Manual"
.SH NAME
l10n-preview - Preview translations in simulated UI elements
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B l10n-preview
.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBl10n-preview\fR is a GTK4/Adwaita application for previewing translation files with simulated UI elements and quality indicators. It opens .po and .ts files, renders strings as simulated buttons, menus, dialogs, and labels, highlights truncated strings, shows source vs translation side by side, and provides filtering and search.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-help
Show help message and exit.
.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.config/l10n-preview/
Configuration files.
.TP
.I ~/.cache/l10n-preview/
Cached data.
